46:18.491 --> 46:21.181
all the time busy with lust and greed,

46:21.546 --> 46:23.346
the children cannot be good children.

46:35.586 --> 46:36.706
They cannot represent

46:37.011 --> 46:39.161
Ganesha tatwa as it should be.

