This should give you

47:14.411 --> 47:15.821
the power of innocence,

47:16.271 --> 47:19.231
the power of purity,

47:19.231 --> 47:20.231
the power of wisdom.

47:30.561 --> 47:33.711
It should give you the art of playfulness of joy.

47:46.121 --> 47:53.051
